snippet.title: Castlevania: Seal of the Eclipse -- Fan Project Teaser
snippet.description:
Obligatory disclaimer due to professional courtesy as well as not to even allow the potential for any current or future confusion about officiality or anything of the like: This is a fan-developed work and all assets and production thereof are not endorsed by or otherwise affiliated with Konami. 

I'm pleased as pie to finally let this cat out of the bag -- there's a lot of info to explain and a Youtube descrip is a terrible place for so much info, so for those interested in details please consult the corresponding thread on the Dungeon: https://castlevaniadungeon.net/forums/index.php?topic=10015

Please follow https://twitter.com/demoncastlewar for future updates/news about the project as well.
